description: Rare opportunity to own this recently refreshed penthouse condo centrally located in the heart of the East Side! This meticulously maintained unit features an updated kitchen with gas range, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, shaker cabinets, custom tiled backsplash and opens to the adjacent living space. The well thought out open floor plan feels bright and spacious with cathedral ceilings, a skylight, and a separate dining area. The updated stylish bathroom includes stackable laundry and a linen closet. The oversized bedroom is flooded with light through the bay windows and has double closet with custom built organizer. Hardwood flooring, central AC, a gas fireplace, recessed lighting, fresh paint, and a private back deck complete this unit. All this only a few blocks to the beach and all of the shops and restaurants East Broadway has to offer!! Please see feature sheet for all updates!
